metadata.name: Coralia [Glass Sculpture]
metadata.description:
This NFT comes together with the physical glass sculpture.

Coralia glass sculpture can be used as a display object and can also be proposed as a jewelry dish. The sculpture is handcrafted and intended to bring joy into our homes.

The glass sculpture is currently exhibited at Nationale Gallery in Portland Oregon, USA. In 2020 was part of the Never Normal exhibition in Detroit, Michigan.
